 the one he gets matched up with hates his guts and the feelings mutual . Obviously they start to like one another , but both way to stubborn to admit it . But .. Genma has a history of doing this . He promised Ranma to many girls . < br /><br />Trust me . It 's worth watching . It 's humorous , heartwarming and all around amazing .
